<DataTransferItemGetAsFileSystemHandle>
<summary>
The <strong><c>getAsFileSystemHandle()</c></strong> method of the<br/><see cref="DataTransferItem"/> interface returns a <see cref="'FileSystemFileHandle'"/><br/>if the dragged item is a file, or a <see cref="'FileSystemDirectoryHandle'"/> if the<br/>dragged item is a directory.
</summary>
<remarks>
<para>-<see href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/File_System_Access_API">File System Access API</see><br/>-<see href="https://web.dev/file-system-access/">The File System Access API: simplifying access to local files</see><br/></para>
<para><seealso href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransferItem/getAsFileSystemHandle"> <em>See also on MDN</em> </seealso></para>
</remarks>
<returns>A {{jsxref('Promise')}} fulfilled with a <see cref="'FileSystemFileHandle'"/> or <see cref="'FileSystemDirectoryHandle'"/>.</returns>
</DataTransferItemGetAsFileSystemHandle>
